description: Jed Holdredge is Owner/Instructor/Chef of Tapas Bravas, the only authentic Spanish cuisine in Central Texas, serving small plates of classic Spanish tapas and sangría setups out of a newly outfitted vintage bread delivery truck in a shaded courtyard. Tapas Bravas also offers catering, as well as instructional and hands-on cooking class events. Based on recipes and techniques from Jed’s time living in and travelling throughout Spain.To get the word straight from Jed on how the truck came to be, some of the best bites to get, and why tapas, read the Roaming Hunger interview here: http://roaminghunger.com/blog/4645/brava-to-tapas-bravas
name: Tapas Bravas
